# .crewrig/.synced-markers/ — adopt-on-edit sync state (spec 0020)
#
# Holds one file per adopt-on-edit path: <path>.sha containing the upstream
# blob SHA the last successful sync applied. Machine-managed by
# scripts/sync-from-upstream.sh — DO NOT hand-edit.
#
# Committed by the adopter (durable across a fresh clone, so the "modified?"
# verdict survives), but carved out of the upstream sync guard and restore
# (policy `excluded` under the strict `.crewrig` parent) so it never aborts a
# sync nor gets clobbered. Ships empty upstream.
